---
// Invite component with call to action
---

<section class="py-20 px-6 bg-wmg-bg">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-wmg-text/90 leading-relaxed fade-up">
      We invite all men who feel the call to join us and voyage deeper into the mysteries of life and  manhood.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;
  }
  
  .fade-up.reveal {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
</style>
